race.comment: Former Victorian LAUNCHER (7) has been thereabouts in all three runs since joining the new stable and looks to be on the doorstep of a maiden victory. Ready to peak now fourth-up from the break and rates the one they all have to run down. DOINGITEASY (3) has hit the top-four in all three runs this time in work and looks well placed against this line-up. Genuine top-three prospects. ANDROS (1) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in four of his past five outings. A must for the multiples. HOMELAND (4) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets some weight relief with the claim. In the mix.
